According to the Game of Thrones books, Valyrian steel is a super strong and light metal forged when the Valyrians governed Essos . 
  It was said to have been lost with the Doom of Valyria  . 
  Ryan Consell studied the composition of modern steel and welding techniques . 
  He concludes Valyri steel is not a steel at all but a metal matrix composite . 
  The findings were made in a video for the American Chemical Society . 
 